{"tid":1945512,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★疫情下無街去　Netflix 觀看人數太高導致死 server","createTime":"2020-03-27T06:07:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T09:53:06.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"363b48c3ab60d0b80de058cc0ab3290f60f43c87","tid":1945512,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/20200326/319878291798495232.png/uhZl-1t0EcA1Y5QvJjLpOQf9CXk_PQAzaUZoSGlGaEg?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F20200326%2F319878291798495232.png%2FuhZl-1t0EcA1Y5QvJjLpOQf9CXk_PQAzaUZoSGlGaEg%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=1a4eb698&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎 令Netflix死機？】（新冠肺炎、COVID-19）為了減低受感染的風險，或減少口罩的消耗，很多人都選擇留在家中，而打機和觀看串流平台的節目，成為消磨時間的最好辦法。Netflix 亦因此吸引到更多「信眾」加入，同時上線的人數也一直高企，更令到 Netflix 在 26 日凌晨發生斷線的情況。<br />\n<br />\nNetflix 死 ser 世界末日！<br />\n<br />\n不論是《Stranger Things》﹑《愛的迫降》還是《Ultraman》，Netflix 的節目總有一樣是吸引到觀眾，在武漢肺炎疫情下更是加快了 Netflix 的觀眾增長。但正因為觀眾人數過多，在香港時間 26 日凌晨突然拒絕加載，部份 Netflix 用家不能進行網站，就算改用平板電腦﹑手機或電視都是同一個情況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/453022/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E4%B8%8B%E7%84%A1%E8%A1%97%E5%8E%BB-netflix-%E8%A7%80%E7%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E5%A4%AA%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%8E%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%BB-server\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2595%25B8%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B4%25BB%2F453022%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E4%25B8%258B%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25A1%2597%25E5%258E%25BB-netflix-%25E8%25A7%2580%25E7%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B0%258E%25E8%2587%25B4%25E6%25AD%25BB-server&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNsFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=6456db29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/453022/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E4%B8%8B%E7%84%A1%E8%A1%97%E5%8E%BB-netflix-%E8%A7%80%E7%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E5%A4%AA%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%8E%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%BB-server</a>"},{"pid":"8e833616f2344b88cd936a43bb615230b0389906","tid":1945512,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:07:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7747308dd74678e0019a87ec11d14b7afb5b68d","tid":1945512,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:07:40.000Z","msg":"World No IT"},{"pid":"caed6ba357f773e49fa81a4ea8cdef5551cf0228","tid":1945512,"uid":8014,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:09:11.000Z","msg":"屌你啦 我有交月費架<br />\n<br />\n你要穩定提供服務好基本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37669250af3d9082cf5a752c2add5c0a93fc78ea","tid":1945512,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:10:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd3d6b8c1341ba77748054871dd71b75efa4c82","tid":1945512,"uid":160662,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:10:39.000Z","msg":"凌晨? 唔駛番工都唔代表唔駛訓掛, 多得過午夜前?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申: 好順未斷過"},{"pid":"5711b5ea15cf708a5d6c3b96036374844cddebf7","tid":1945512,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"caed6ba357f773e49fa81a4ea8cdef5551cf0228","tid":1945512,"uid":8014,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:09:11.000Z","ms